{"tid":415254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海外專家指恐襲防不勝防　籲港策劃人教育參加者安全措施應對危機","createTime":"2017-09-26T23:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T00:00:57.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40d87bcf91b458b830772ebf50f9ee89b367423b","tid":415254,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/121281/thumbnail/64ee2280e547c65682944247d09ce990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F121281%2Fthumbnail%2F64ee2280e547c65682944247d09ce990.jpg&h=41fc9ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年5月歌手Ariana Grande於英國曼徹斯特音樂會遭受恐怖襲擊，她上周來港演唱時場館加強保安，活動順利舉行。不過孤狼式恐襲連連，有海外活動安全策劃顧問表示恐襲無法預防，只可盡量執法單位堵塞漏洞，並持續教育公眾。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前在西九文化區舉行的電子音樂節中，有人疑服毒品後身亡，專家指各地不少活動都有濫藥問題，會安排工作犬及輔導專家進場監察，更會運用科技狙擊毒販。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/780029/xlarge/bd8d62303069d2c6fe7036656d21a8c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F780029%2Fxlarge%2Fbd8d62303069d2c6fe7036656d21a8c0.jpg&h=574a4c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界經歷多番恐襲，但各地民眾拒絕消極面對挑戰。（路透社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/858379/xlarge/d5703b9e210cabd215e837d0a5537b78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F858379%2Fxlarge%2Fd5703b9e210cabd215e837d0a5537b78.jpg&h=ebb71ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海外專家的Tim Roberts（右） 及Jon Corbishley分別曾為上百萬人參與活動的籌劃安全管理，指只要活動單位及個人處理好應對風險，可令活動避免成為恐襲目標。林楚釗(左)則指港人應多參考事故下應對方案，有所防範。（邱靖汶攝）<br />\n<br />\n近年歐美不少大型活動成為恐怖分子襲擊目標，憑大規模傷亡來吸引國際間悲傷而憤怒的眼球。曾為戴安娜葬禮及英女王金禧活動統籌人群安全、來自澳洲的Jon Corbishley，與音樂節、體育賽事等擔任英籍安全顧問的Tim Roberts分享經驗時，指打擊恐怖主義是國際層面的一大挑戰。雖然企業及個人層面難防範恐襲，但大型活動策劃人應盡量做足防預措施，包括應疏散速度設立入場上限、入場檢查隨身物品等。「越來越多活動不准帶手提包，大家已開始習慣，甚至有20多歲青年投訴音樂會安檢不足。」他們建議各活動舉辦人可透過社交網站提醒參加者安全須知，教育他們措施只為確保安全，大家可在活動上盡歡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/858349/xlarge/609c388611479dde04a22771a36aea09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F858349%2Fxlarge%2F609c388611479dde04a22771a36aea09.jpg&h=59d17489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專家指兒童活動最易失控，觀眾層較成熟的音樂會風險較低。(Getty Images)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/693035/xlarge/4a7e497abdc7e8d859a7df4861ce6212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F693035%2Fxlarge%2F4a7e497abdc7e8d859a7df4861ce6212.jpg&h=1d64366b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/593015/xlarge/24f98b435016704e39c3ee9819c261d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F593015%2Fxlarge%2F24f98b435016704e39c3ee9819c261d2.jpg&h=747017e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/670901/xlarge/505d1ad5fda0af05f31b13bdb6fa7268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F670901%2Fxlarge%2F505d1ad5fda0af05f31b13bdb6fa7268.jpg&h=0dfdc764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/25361/xlarge/8f405bfdb0c4d4cdae7f4a6e18202271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F25361%2Fxlarge%2F8f405bfdb0c4d4cdae7f4a6e18202271.jpg&h=36865188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/155733/xlarge/31e7331181216628b8adbaf922bf14f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F155733%2Fxlarge%2F31e7331181216628b8adbaf922bf14f4.jpg&h=3db3b05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/778734/xlarge/4ff8fb98e1453c02bb3d5c491a9790fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F778734%2Fxlarge%2F4ff8fb98e1453c02bb3d5c491a9790fe.jpg&h=63911f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/780027/xlarge/03e0a32f0b059f7deed17660f7772e32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F780027%2Fxlarge%2F03e0a32f0b059f7deed17660f7772e32.jpg&h=6c6164a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/619905/xlarge/5a1143433796cb89b43c54f3b94c78eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F619905%2Fxlarge%2F5a1143433796cb89b43c54f3b94c78eb.jpg&h=35a39687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/448428/xlarge/c630e62a4db2f17183bae203f3e7127d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F448428%2Fxlarge%2Fc630e62a4db2f17183bae203f3e7127d.jpg&h=99c3eb79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多方面搗場內濫藥<br />\n<br />\n早前在西九文化區舉行的電子音樂節中，懷疑有人服用毒品後傷亡，海外專家不評論事件，但指外地不少活動有毒品問題，除了靠入場安檢堵截毒販「帶貨」入場，也會用閉路電視面容技術識別可疑行為，例如經常出入洗手間及有金錢交易，場內也會有毒品調查犬。但這些方法只能治標，故專業心理輔導員在會場內尋找「目標」，從根本心態叫停不當行為。<br />\n<br />\n兒童表演最難搞　搖滾粉絲成熟有序<br />\n<br />\n在探討防災及恐襲等嚴肅問題，不論受訪者與記者都一臉凝重，但被問到多年來遇過最棘手的活動，兩名專家對望後尷尬苦笑，全臉通紅：「卡通人物巡迴展！」「場地內太多幼童，他們見到卡通人物出來便衝前、尖叫，忘形到忘了找媽媽和上洗手間。」雖然情況難纏，但只要活動單位及早評估風險，一切都是可控制的情況。「重金屬搖滾音樂會的觀眾雖然吵鬧，但他們較成熟，懂得應對突發處境，活動風險低。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/841381/xlarge/646b24a7cdbd7553ff90e25abcd16dea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F841381%2Fxlarge%2F646b24a7cdbd7553ff90e25abcd16dea.jpg&h=2bf65300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電子音樂節「Road to Ultra」早前在西九文化區苗圃公園露天場地舉行。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1846/xlarge/00329803cf9411d30b69da2a3326cec5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1846%2Fxlarge%2F00329803cf9411d30b69da2a3326cec5.jpg&h=f8f39a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘭桂坊於1993年元旦發生人踩人悲劇。（資料圖片/2016年元旦倒數）"},{"pid":"2d9df3956f16b63a89283faa4e4221ebdb546ad1","tid":415254,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"港人外遊前應評風險學應變<br />\n<br />\n幸運地，香港至今未曾發生恐襲，不過維持中度風險。賽馬會災難防護應變教研中心總監林楚釗指，恐怖襲擊成為全球新挑戰，無處不在，港人也難置身事外，故邀請海外專家與業界分享心得。她又提到港人愛外遊，近日多了人參與海外馬拉松等活動，建議參與者要評估風險，並預先了解各項事故的自保措拖；如遇上人踩人最好靠牆站，即使跌倒亦要盡力保護頭部及胸腔等，並配合主辦單位的指示。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：邱靖汶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/121281/%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%9D%E9%98%B2-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E8%80%85%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F121281%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%2598%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258B%259D%25E9%2598%25B2-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E5%258A%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F&d=ET79mwu14G5d3JvAXnBCiP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a813512e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/121281/%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%9D%E9%98%B2-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E8%80%85%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"8ffca02f743bcef7b530838547531690fccfdf44","tid":415254,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fkpa4voi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffkpa4voi&h=5579f572&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}